OL,5, Over 100 more former and current       
OL,6, McDonald's workers have come forward to
OL,7, allege they faced harassment and       
OL,8, bullying at the chain, following a BBC 
OL,9, investigation.                         
OL,11,FThe BBC's probe that found workers as  
OL,12,Fyoung as 17 claiming they were being   
OL,13,Fgroped and harassed almost routinely.  
OL,15,FNow more stories are surfacing, putting
OL,16,Ffurther pressure on McDonald's.        
OL,18,FThe chain said it had "stringent"      
OL,19,Fstandards and would investigate all    
OL,20,Fallegations brought to it.             
